titleInfo.title: Report of the Board of Park Commissioners

name.namePart: Cuts by H.E. Northrup Co., Memphis

physicalDescription.extent: 34 loose pages: 2 color and 32 black & white

mods.abstract: Pages from the Report of the Board of Park Commissioners of Memphis, Tennessee, covering the years of 1913 to 1915. Document includes photos of former and present Park Commissioners, reports from multiple roleplayers, inventories, budgets, donor lists, photographs of parks and statistics. (NOTE: Original document dismantled. Some pages may be missing or out of order.)
